column3: “Happy, relaxing strain without putting you out. Good for listening to music, concerts, creative events and activities. Fuzzy head, anti-nausea, anti-anxiety.”
“Quick-acting, and made me want to dance. I listened intently to a child and played with a dog. Good stuff.”
“So good! All levels! Eleviates depression, stress, pain in all forms, and invokes a little sexy time ;)”
